Perform Analysis: Utilize SQL to perform the analysis and answer the questions mentioned in the case studies. Ensure that you understand the table structures and the meaning of various columns such as event types and what to consider for reviewing.
Submit a Report: Prepare a report (PDF/PPT) to present your findings to the leadership team. The report should include the following details:

